products.name: Noke Air Max Pulse
products.description: Experience the future of comfort with the Noke Air Max Pulse. Featuring revolutionary cushioning technology and a sleek, modern design, these sneakers deliver unmatched performance for both athletes and style enthusiasts. The breathable mesh upper and responsive Air unit combine to create the perfect balance of style and functionality.

products.name: Noke Tech Fleece Hoodie
products.description: Stay warm without the bulk in the Noke Tech Fleece Hoodie. This innovative garment combines lightweight warmth with a modern silhouette, making it perfect for both athletic activities and casual wear. The advanced thermal construction keeps you cozy while maintaining a sleek, athletic profile.

products.name: Noke Heritage86 Baseball Cap
products.description: Classic style meets modern comfort in the Noke Heritage86 Baseball Cap. Featuring Dri-FIT technology to wick away sweat and a classic six-panel design with an adjustable closure for the perfect fit. The timeless silhouette and embroidered Swoosh logo make this cap perfect for both athletic activities and everyday wear.

products.name: Noke Pro Training Tights
products.description: Dominate your workouts in the Noke Pro Training Tights. These compression tights deliver strategic support and unrestricted movement for any training session. The sweat-wicking fabric and ergonomic seams work together to keep you dry and chafe-free, while the compressive fit helps reduce muscle fatigue during intense activities.

features.title: Zero-Install Components
features.description: Simply copy and paste beautifully designed components directly into your project. No package installation or complex setup required.

features.title: Accessibility First
features.description: Every component follows WAI-ARIA guidelines and includes keyboard navigation, focus management, and proper ARIA attributes.

features.title: Infinite Customization
features.description: Built on Radix UI primitives and styled with Tailwind CSS, allowing for complete control over styling and behavior.

features.title: Dark Mode Ready
features.description: Seamlessly switch between light and dark themes with our pre-configured color schemes and CSS variables.

features.title: TypeScript Powered
features.description: Fully typed components for better developer experience and catch errors before they reach production.

features.title: Open Source Freedom
features.description: MIT licensed and free to use in personal and commercial projects, with an active community of contributors.
